data.description: Gorgeous all brick ranch!  Newer windows, roof, a/c, water heater and dishwasher!  Every room has a ceiling fan!  The laundry shoot is a fun unique feature! Laundry located in basement!  Tanning Bed stays along with washer and dryer!  Hurry this beautiful one story home located in the heart of Jerome won’t last long!  All showings must have a licensed realtor and pre approval letter!
data.whatILove: Privacy fenced in yard, plenty of outlets in every room, no carpet, ceiling fan in every room, laundry shoot, fireplace in the basement along with a tanning bed!
